high_descs: Move to the black table.
Pick up the pencil from the black table.
Bring the pencil to the box on the chair.
Put the pencil in the box.
Pick up the box from the chair.
Bring the box to the coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the box with pencil on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step, then turn right and walk up to the small black table with a pencil on it.
Pick up the pencil off of the black table.
Turn around and walk over to the coffee table, then turn right and walk up to the chair with a cardboard box on the seat.
Place the pencil inside the cardboard box.
Pick up the cardboard box with a pencil inside.
Turn left and walk over to the fireplace, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Place the cardboard box with a pencil inside onto the coffee table to the right of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Place a cardboard box with a pencil inside it onto the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the dresser.
Pick up the pencil on the dresser.
Turn around and head towards the sofa chair with the box on your right.
Place the pencil inside the box.
Pick up the box from the sofa.
Turn left, walk past the table, turn left and look on to the table.
Place the box next to the laptop on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the box with a pencil on the table.
